[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0376","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0376.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0193","title":"3Com 路由器 TCP 零长选项拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ascend 与 3Com 路由器在处理特殊构造的 TCP 数据包时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标路由器发送包含零长度 TCP 选项（Zero Length TCP Option）的恶意数据包，触发设备处理异常导致路由器强制重启或崩溃。该漏洞影响 Ascend R 4.5 Ci12 及部分 3Com 路由器版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。目前厂商已发布固件更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0193"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:52.973","remediation":"建议升级 Ascend Router 固件至 4.5 Ci12 之后的修复版本，或升级 3Com 路由器至厂商发布的修补固件。若暂时无法升级，可在边界防火墙配置规则丢弃 TCP 选项长度为 0 的异常数据包，同时启用 TCP 状态检测功能缓解攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0193","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20332","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0193","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0193.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5p2w-742f-cg75/GHSA-5p2w-742f-cg75.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000239.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0376.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0429","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0429.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0244","title":"Livingston RADIUS 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Livingston RADIUS 实现存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 RADIUS 认证服务发送特制数据包触发缓冲区溢出，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响多个 Livingston 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至最新版本或部署访问控制列表限制 RADIUS 服务访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0244"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.367","remediation":"立即升级 Livingston RADIUS 至 2.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 RADIUS 代码中的栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。对于无法升级的旧系统，应在边界防火墙上限制对 RADIUS UDP 端口 1812/1645 的访问来源，仅允许受信任的 NAS 设备 IP 接入。建议迁移至当前仍受支持的 RADIUS 实现（如 FreeRADIUS 3.x），并在运行 RADIUS 服务的主机上启用栈缓冲区溢出保护机制（如 ASLR、NX）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0244","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0244.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0244","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0244.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0244.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4912a395-3fc6-4764-84b7-7d315af3698f.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0429.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0559","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0559.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0340","title":"Slackware Linux crond 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux Slackware 系统中 crond 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户可通过向 crond 程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞允许拥有本地账户的攻击者利用 crond 在处理参数时的内存边界校验缺陷，实现权限提升。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，影响 Slackware Linux 系统。建议用户升级至修复版本或限制本地用户对 crond 的访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0340"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.243","remediation":"升级 Slackware Linux 至 3.4 及以上版本，该修复版本已修正 crond 程序在处理用户提交的计划任务参数时的边界检查缺陷，防止本地用户通过特制参数触发缓冲区溢出提权。如无法升级，可限制 crond 仅允许受信用户通过 `cron.allow` 文件控制访问，并移除 `/etc/cron.d` 中不必要的任务文件。同时检查 crond 二进制是否被替换，使用 `rpm -V` 或 `md5sum` 校验文件完整性。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0340"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0559.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0056","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0056.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0016","title":"多厂商 TCP Land 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Land 攻击是一种经典的拒绝服务攻击方式。攻击者向目标主机发送一个特制的 TCP SYN 数据包，其中源 IP 地址、源端口与目的 IP 地址、目的端口完全相同。目标主机收到后试图与自己建立 TCP 连接，导致操作系统陷入无限自应答循环，最终耗尽 CPU 资源造成系统崩溃或挂起。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0、Linux 2.0.34 以下版本、FreeBSD 2.2.6 以下版本、HP-UX、NetBSD 等多个主流操作系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0016"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到已修复版本：Windows NT 4.0 安装 Service Pack 4 及以上，Linux 升级内核至 2.0.34 及以上，FreeBSD 升级至 2.2.6 及以上，NetBSD 升级至 1.3.2 及以上，HP-UX 安装对应 PHNE 补丁。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙/路由器上配置 ACL 策略，丢弃源 IP 与目的 IP 相同的入站 TCP SYN 数据包，同时启用基于 RFC 2827 的入口过滤以防止 IP 地址欺骗。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9801-076","https://security.netapp.com/advisory/ntap-20170815-0001/","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20814","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0016.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/1fb9a053a31c41206e693c4b4856611d722d4df7/1999/CVE-1999-0016.json","https://github.com/mthcht/awesome-lists/blob/20bccdfe36ad7e2a6c15ebfa83f10e46b5864396/Lists/Others/Defender_yara_rules/Win32/Exploit/CVE-1999-0016.yara","https://github.com/roadwy/DefenderYara/blob/59e39903d9e6667c7c3e55a1f2887f1faab0e423/Exploit/Win32/CVE-1999-0016/Exploit_Win32_CVE-1999-0016_MR_MTB.yar","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/bef4442939206e97bbfee4995afab3b6c8a2377c/1999/CVE-1999-0016/README.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0016","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/c8b30957414aefbd6ba0b766db0d40593ba36fba/references/CVE-1999-0016-2023-09-21-1730","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/diannaofengzi/POC/blob/14d504f7488db9229f6f02be54aab53e3cfee0dc/databases/1999/database/CVE-1999-0016/CVE-1999-0016-POC-Pommaq.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest/blob/8829fba0b0ee59d68a105191067da3a7b4aa27de/references/contrib1-CVE-1999-0016-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/pexmee/CVE-1999-0016-Land-DOS-tool","https://github.com/Pommaq/CVE-1999-0016-POC"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0056.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0396","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0396.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0210","title":"Sun Microsystems Solaris automountd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 系统中的自动挂载守护进程 automountd 存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞，本地或远程攻击者可通过向 automountd 传递包含特殊 shell 字符的恶意请求，诱使系统以提升的权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5.1 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可触发利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0210"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-11-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.103","remediation":"立即安装 Sun 官方补丁：Solaris 2.5.1 SPARC 平台安装 103613-01 或更新版本，x86 平台安装 103612-01 或更新版本；Solaris 2.6 用户安装对应内核补丁。如无法立即升级，可在 `/etc/init.d/autofs` 中停止 automountd 服务并禁用自启动（`/etc/init.d/autofs stop; rm /etc/rc3.d/S74autofs`），同时在 `/etc/hosts.equiv` 和 `netgroup` 中限制可访问 automount 资源的主机范围作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88053459921223&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91547759121289&w=2","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-99-05-statd-automountd.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/235","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9910-104","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19199","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0210.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0210.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0210","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0210.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0210.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-63gj-m3j5-p47q/GHSA-63gj-m3j5-p47q.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rpc_automountd.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0396.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0068","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0068.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0021","title":"Muhammad A. Muquit wwwcount 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"wwwcount 的 Count.cgi 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 wwwcount 2.3 及更早版本，攻击无需身份认证，危害等级高，CVSS 评分 7.5。通过向 Count.cgi 传入超长参数即可触发栈溢出，从而实现远程代码执行或拒绝服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0021"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-11-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.013","remediation":"升级 wwwcount 至 2.4 及以上版本，或从 CGI 目录移除 Count.cgi 脚本。若无法升级，在 Web 服务器层面添加输入过滤规则，限制对 Count.cgi 的参数长度（如 Apache ModSecurity 限制 QUERY_STRING 不超过 256 字节），并确保以最低权限运行 CGI 程序。同时可在 Web 服务器访问控制中限制 Count.cgi 仅允许信任的来源 IP 调用，降低被远程利用的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/128","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19105","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0021.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0021","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0021.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0021.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0021.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jfr4-hpqv-2pq4/GHSA-jfr4-hpqv-2pq4.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/count_cgi.nasl","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/1149.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0068.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0511","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0511.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0306","title":"HP-UX xlock 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统中的 xlock 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可以通过向 xlock 程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，导致攻击者能够以 root 权限执行任意代码，从而完全控制受影响的系统。攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0306"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-11-04","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 系统至包含安全补丁的最新版本，限制非授权用户对 xlock 程序的执行权限，并监控系统日志中的异常提权行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:15:41.755870705+00:00","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0306"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0511.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0403","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0403.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0216","title":"Linux Kernel inetd SYN/RST Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 版本的 inetd 超级服务守护进程存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标主机发送特制的 SYN 和 RST 数据包，导致 inetd 服务异常终止或资源耗尽，无法正常响应合法连接请求。该漏洞影响运行 inetd 服务的 Linux 系统，攻击者无需认证即可实施攻击，且无需目标系统上存在特定监听服务。利用方式简单，通过发送大量伪造的 TCP SYN/RST 包即可触发，属于典型的网络层拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0216"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.917","remediation":"建议将 legacy inetd 替换为 xinetd，并在配置中设置 per_source = 5、cps = 25 30、max_load = 3 以限制并发连接和速率。或者迁移至 systemd socket 激活机制，利用内核 SYN cookies（sysctl -w net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies=1）和 iptables/nftables 限制入站 SYN 包速率（如 iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --syn -m limit --limit 10/s -j ACCEPT）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0216","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0216","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0216.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g7qq-2qq9-j34m/GHSA-g7qq-2qq9-j34m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0216.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2bbcf0ff-3ba8-4c91-aea6-e3d5fdb0e178.json","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/linux.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0403.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0542","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0542.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0327","title":"SGI IRIX syserr 本地文件破坏漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统的 syserr 程序存在文件处理缺陷，本地攻击者可利用该程序以系统权限破坏或覆盖任意文件，导致系统不稳定或拒绝服务。该漏洞仅需本地用户账户即可触发，无需特殊权限，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0327"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.697","remediation":"立即应用 SGI 安全公告 19971103-01-PX 提供的官方补丁。由于 SGI IRIX 已于 2013 年底停止技术支持，长期建议迁移至仍在维护的 Linux 或 BSD 操作系统。临时缓解措施：以 root 身份执行 `chmod 755 /usr/sbin/syserr` 移除 setuid 权限位，并通过 `chgrp` 将 syserr 程序组改为仅受信任的管理员组，限制普通用户执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0542.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0543","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0543.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0328","title":"SGI IRIX permissions 程序缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 5.x 和 6.x 系统中 /usr/lib/desktop/permissions 程序存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向该程序提供超长且精心构造的第4个参数，触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 sys 组权限执行任意代码。该漏洞已有公开利用代码，由 David Hedley 于 1997年5月发布。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0328"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-11-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即应用 SGI 安全公告 19971103-01-PX 中提供的补丁，升级 permissions 程序。如无法打补丁，应移除 permissions 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/lib/desktop/permissions），并严格限制可登录系统的本地用户账号，仅保留受信任的管理员用户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0328","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19318"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19318"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0543.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0217","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0217.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0092","title":"IBM AIX 4.2.1 portmir 本地缓冲区溢出与不安全的临时文件创建漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.2.1 系统中的 /usr/bin/portmir 命令存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者可通过向该命令传递特制超长参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址以执行任意代码；同时该命令还存在不安全的临时文件创建问题，攻击者可利用符号链接竞争条件劫持临时文件实现提权。本地攻击者在拥有普通用户权限的条件下即可利用此漏洞获得 root 权限，影响 IBM AIX 4.2.1 及更早版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0092"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.030","remediation":"立即升级至 IBM AIX 5.1 及以上受支持版本，该问题已在后续版本中得到修复。如无法升级，以 root 执行 chmod 0755 /usr/bin/portmir 去除 setuid 位，并移除其他用户执行权限：chown root:system /usr/bin/portmir；同时在 /etc/security/sysck.cfg 中移除 portmir 条目标记。临时缓解措施可将需要 portmir 功能的用户加入专用组，通过 sudo 授权最小权限使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0092","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19306","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0092","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0092.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-673v-6c89-8w4x/GHSA-673v-6c89-8w4x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4be848c8-03f3-452a-a9ce-ef9613324759.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0217.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0219","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0219.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0093","title":"IBM AIX nslookup 命令本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统自带的 nslookup 命令在执行过程中未能正确清除提升的特权，导致本地普通用户可通过调用该命令获得 root 权限。攻击者只需拥有系统本地访问权限即可利用此漏洞，无需身份认证或用户交互。该漏洞影响多个 AIX 发行版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级 AIX 操作系统至厂商已修复的最新版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0093"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.180","remediation":"建议立即安装 IBM 针对此漏洞发布的 APAR 补丁（IX73355），将 bos.net.tcp.client 文件集更新至 4.3.2.0 或更高版本。临时缓解措施可移除 nslookup 命令的 setuid root 权限：chmod u-s /usr/bin/nslookup。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0219.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0221","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0221.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0094","title":"IBM AIX piodmgrsu 命令本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 操作系统中 piodmgrsu 命令存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用该命令对用户组权限验证的缺陷，在未获得授权的情况下获取额外的用户组权限，从而扩大系统访问范围，执行越权操作。该漏洞影响多个 AIX 版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0094"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.320","remediation":"安装 IBM 提供的对应 APAR 补丁（如 IX66020），或移除 piodmgrsu 命令的 setgid 权限（chmod g-s /usr/bin/piodmgrsu），并限制仅授权管理员可执行，防止本地用户利用此命令获取额外组权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0094"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0221.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0228","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0228.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0097","title":"IBM AIX FTP 客户端命令注入漏洞","description":"AIX FTP 客户端在处理来自恶意 FTP 服务器的响应时存在命令注入漏洞。攻击者通过在 FTP 协议响应中嵌入 shell 元字符（如管道符 |），当用户连接至攻击者控制的 FTP 服务器时，恶意内容被传递给 shell 执行，导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可完全控制受害系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0097"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.750","remediation":"建议升级至 AIX 4.3.3 及以上维护版本，或安装 IBM APAR 安全补丁（IX72452 / IY07246）。如无法升级，可使用 OpenSSH sftp 替代 ftp 命令进行文件传输，或在 /usr/bin/ftp 上通过 chmod 移除不必要的执行权限以限制使用。避免使用 AIX ftp 客户端连接不可信或不受控的 FTP 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0097"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0228.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0536","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0536.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0322","title":"FreeBSD open() 函数本地任意文件写入漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 操作系统的 open() 函数存在权限检查缺陷，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞以提升的权限向任意文件执行写入操作。该漏洞影响早期版本的 FreeBSD 系统，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限。由于漏洞利用需要本地账户，CVSS 评分仅为 2.1，危害等级较低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0322"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.983","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 系统至 3.0-RELEASE 或更高版本，该版本已修复 open() 系统调用中因缺乏权限检查导致的任意文件写入问题。如无法升级，可通过 sysctl 设置 kern.securelevel=1 提高内核安全等级，限制非 root 用户对敏感文件的 open 调用，并严格管控本地用户的可信度。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6092"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0536.toml"}]